<p>Hello, <%= @user.email %>!</p>

<p>We received a request to promote <strong><%= @target.email %></strong> to owner of
<strong><%= @organization.name %></strong>.</p>

<p>Your confirmation code is:</p>

<p style="font-size:28px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:4px"><%= @code %></p>

<p>Enter this code on the promotion confirmation screen. It expires in 30 minutes.</p>

<p>If you did not request this, ignore this email - <%= @target.email %> will not be promoted
unless you complete the confirmation.</p>
